689
00:21:22,070 --> 00:21:23,400
The first prize! First prize!

690
00:21:23,400 --> 00:21:24,600
I won the first prize!

691
00:21:24,610 --> 00:21:25,540
The first prize!

692
00:21:26,750 --> 00:21:27,950
I got the first prize!

693
